query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-context',
'attr',
'databricks',
'file-rename',
'ieee-754',
'interceptor',
'objective-c++',
'phone-call',
'postgresql-9.3',
'quickblox',
'tablelayout');
